title: "EigenCV: Zero-Trust Agentic Resume Pipeline"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: "2026-06-07"
url: "https://bourier.biz"
abstract: >-
  EigenCV is a Zero-Trust Agentic Resume Pipeline and Infrastructure-as-Code (IaC) tool designed to generate ATS-optimized LaTeX resumes while strictly preventing LLM hallucinations. It treats a user's career history as an immutable offline JSON database, utilizing AI solely as a semantic retrieval and orchestration layer rather than a content generator. By implementing an EigenTruth Engine (a deterministic verification system) and strict Pydantic schemas, it intercepts and prevents AI-injected skills or fabricated data. This ensures 100% factual accuracy and data integrity while dynamically compiling targeted applications via pdflatex.